reviews.comment: Order was delivered as promised and statistics are as expected. Views on our song increased and we've gained few new subscribers. Not sure about how organic these views are, our song received some generic comments like "Awesome video" when the video is just the song and a picture, but views and subscribers definitely did increase. Would recommend if you need a little boost for your video for a reasonable price.

So I’m new YouTube like a lot of people I assume visiting this gig are and can I say Mehr went above and beyond. He’s attentive and really easy to communicate with. I Have checked everything seems organic and this boost also allowed me to be featured on YouTube on the home page as well as recommended after section.

Overall very happy:)

Mehrali155 did a great job and even overdelivered the promised view-count.

I will Absolutely contract again for this service.

As with everything on the internet, it's silly to think "build it and they will come." That's where this service adds so much value. Even if you have great content, it may not be seen if it doesn't serve the algorithm, and on YouTube, view count is a critical part of the algorithm.

Seller provided a specific service and on time as advertised. I am not sure if it was all actual listeners or bots or both. During the promotion I saw a realistic spike in subscribers and streams, so I am believing the former.

Very happy with the service. The video went up by 1,00o views and gained new subscribers. Bearing in mind I opted for the cheapest package with a small budget I was very happy with the results and can only imagine how much better the results would be with more investment.
